    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159440/extras/415e9c220bdefd1cf8daa0cfa6df3a24.avif?t=1755140242\" width=789 height=207 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>像素大千世界，水墨战破苍穹。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游历像素风格的修真世界，转场进入手绘风战斗。角色施展招式时行云流水，卡牌特效与人物动作浑然一体——绝非单调的卡牌切换，而是充满张力的动态对决！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159440/extras/0ca9efd5daca7635c3226f6d78f39a99.poster.avif?t=1755140242\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159440/extras/0ca9efd5daca7635c3226f6d78f39a99.webm?t=1755140242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159440/extras/0ca9efd5daca7635c3226f6d78f39a99.mp4?t=1755140242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>光阴似箭，命数如灯——修士最缺的，从来不是机缘，而是时间。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可随时『闭关』：强化卡牌、疗伤破境——然洞中无甲子，每进一步皆折阳寿。是燃命证道，还是稳渡长生？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159440/extras/ea00ec943293b2fb5bccbb421000fc73.poster.avif?t=1755140242\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159440/extras/ea00ec943293b2fb5bccbb421000fc73.webm?t=1755140242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159440/extras/ea00ec943293b2fb5bccbb421000fc73.mp4?t=1755140242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>数百种卡牌、法宝和功法——这才只是修仙之路的开始。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>我在持续更新游戏并随时听取玩家建议，欢迎加入官方QQ群，一起参与游戏的成长与完善！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159440/extras/a815435727b2a3b7b455f7cc256fccd5.poster.avif?t=1755140242\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159440/extras/a815435727b2a3b7b455f7cc256fccd5.webm?t=1755140242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159440/extras/a815435727b2a3b7b455f7cc256fccd5.mp4?t=1755140242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
